<ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Recreational Activities and Special Events, such as popular concert performances,&nbsp;<br /> 	Wii Bowling, Tea Socials and a Cooking Club</li> 	<li>Beauty and Barber Salon</li> 	<li>Bright, Sunny Interior Courtyard</li> 	<li>Ample, Free Parking</li> </ul>  <p style="text-align:start">Social services, counseling and discharge planning are important elements of the care and services Colonial Rehabilitation &amp; Nursing Center provides. Social workers help to identify a residents psycho-social, mental and emotional needs and then develop individualized plans to meet those needs. Discharge planners define additional services and follow-up resources necessary to ensure a smooth transition from the nursing center to home.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><strong><span style="color:rgb(3, 53, 96)">Colonial offers several onsite or nearby continuum of care options including:</span></strong></p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li><a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/assisted-living-ma/weymouth/index" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_self">Allerton House at Central Park Assisted Living</a>&nbsp;care at home after discharge through&nbsp;<a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/homecare-norwell-ma" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_self">Welch Home Care</a>.</li> 	<li><a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/adult-day-health-centers-massachusetts/index" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_self">Colonial Adult Day Health Center</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/senior-living-communities-massachusetts/index" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_self">Colonial Village Apartments</a>, which is&nbsp;designed for independent senior living.</li> </ul>  <p><br /> <br /> <a id="pulm" name="pulm"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Pulmonary Program</strong></span></a></p>  <p style="text-align:start">Colonial now offers comprehensive short-term pulmonary care services to patients with complex pulmonary care requirements, tracheostomy and other pulmonary care needs.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Short-term Pulmonary Care Services Offered at Colonial Include:</p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Licensed respiratory therapist onsite 7-days a week</li> 	<li>Patient education on self-care &amp; prevention of re-hospitalization</li> 	<li>Tracheostomy management &amp; care</li> 	<li>CPAP/BPAP</li> 	<li>Pulmonary vest</li> 	<li>Exercise &amp; skills training</li> 	<li>Nutritional counseling</li> </ul>  <p style="text-align:start">For more detailed information&nbsp;<a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/_pdfs/Colonial_PulmonaryProg_brochure_v11.pdf" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">click here</a>&nbsp;to download our Pulmonary Program brochure.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">&nbsp;</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><a id="shortRehab" name="shortRehab"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Short-term Rehabilitation</strong></span></a></p>  <p style="text-align:start">At Colonial our outstanding short-term rehabilitation programs offer physical, occupational, and speech-language services. Our skilled therapists have expertise in both therapy evaluation and treatment. Services are designed to transition residents from post-acute care to home while maximizing quality of life. Our dedicated team of rehabilitation therapists, nurses, social workers, dieticians and support staff works with each patient and their family to develop a customized care plan designed to meet the patient&rsquo;s individual needs.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> Additionally, Colonial offers three non-invasive and medication-free therapeutic programs through a clinical collaboration with Accelerated Care Plus (ACP). The programs use electrotherapy, ultrasound and shortwave diathermy.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> <a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/_pdfs/Welch-Rehab-Nursing-brochure-v11.pdf" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Click here</a>&nbsp;for our Short-term Rehabilitation brochure</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> <a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/_pdfs/ColonialACP_Therapies_flyer_v6.pdf" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Click here</a>&nbsp;for more detailed information on the ACP Therapeutic Programs</p>  <p style="text-align:start">&nbsp;</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><a id="clinical" name="clinical"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Clinical Services</strong></span></a></p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Subacute Program</li> 	<li>Ostomy Care</li> 	<li>IV Therapy/Central Line Management</li> 	<li>Enteral Tube Feeding</li> 	<li>Wound Care/ Wound Vac</li> 	<li>Diabetic Care and Teaching</li> 	<li>Physical Therapy/Occupational Therapy/Speech and Language Therapy available 7 days/week</li> 	<li>Pleurx Catheter&nbsp;</li> 	<li>Pain Management</li> 	<li>Palliative Care and Hospice</li> 	<li>Admissions 24/7</li> </ul>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> <a id="individService" name="individService"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Individual Services</strong></span></a></p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Complex, multi-diagnosis conditions</li> 	<li>Stroke</li> 	<li>Elective Joint Replacement</li> 	<li>Post-surgical Conditions</li> 	<li>Congestive Heart Failure</li> 	<li>Neurological&nbsp;diseases</li> 	<li>Hip Fracture</li> 	<li>Diabetes</li> 	<li>Pneumonia/Bronchitis/Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</li> 	<li>Limb Loss</li> 	<li>Cancer</li> 	<li>Pain Syndromes</li> </ul> 